<h1>Entry Edit</h1>
<div class="modbox" id="addblog">
  <% form_for :entry, :url => user_entry_path(:id => @entry.id), :html => {:method => :put } do |f|%>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>文章标题:</strong>
      <label>
        <%= f.text_field :title, :class => 'input'%>
      </label>
      <label>
        <%= f.collection_select :entry_category_id, EntryCategory.find(:all), :id, :name %>
      </label>
      </li>
      <li>
      <div id="addblogcon">
        <%= f.text_area :content, :rows => 20, :cols => 70 %>
        </li>
        <li id="tags1"><strong>默认标签:</strong>  <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="att('游戏动漫',this);return false">衣食住行</a></li>
        <li><strong>自己写标签: </strong>
        <input name="tags" id="tags" value="" size="70" type="text">
        </li>
        <li id="tags2" style=""><strong>已有自定义标签:</strong>
        <cite> 提示：点击已有标签可以直接添加至标签栏。多个标签请用空格进行分割。若不填请留空。在博客里，标签等同于文章分类。</cite></li>
        <li class="upload_notice">我们鼓励您上传原创的内容。但请勿上传涉及色情、政治敏感及其他非法内容的文章，否则会被删除。</li>
        <li class="upload_but"><%= submit_tag '立刻发表', :class => 'button' %>
        </li>
      </ul>
    <% end %>
  </div>
